  "title": "Site Engineer",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To supervise Drivers, Operators, General workers and maintenance of equipment at site.</li>\n  <li>Assist and support Project Manager in handling and monitoring smooth progress of project.</li>\n  <li>To ensure and carried out site work in accordance to construction programme safely.</li>\n  <li>Must be familiar with all roads, drainage, sewers and all other infrastructure construction.</li>\n  <li>To carry out all site works issues and ad-hoc duties when instructed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidate to possess relevant certificates and Building Construction Supervisors Safety Course Certificate (BCSS).</li>\n  <li>At least 3 years of working experience in the related field.</li>\n  <li>Preferably with Class 3 Driving licence.</li>\n  <li>Good communication, self-initiative and interpersonal skills.</li>\n</ul>",
